@startuml Sequence Load To Editor
title Workflow: Loading a Report into the UI Editor

actor Client
participant "ReportMaker" as Maker
participant "SavedReport" as DBReport
participant "ReportRequest" as Request
participant "ReportSerializer" as Serializer

Client -> Maker : loadToEditor(reportId)
activate Maker

Maker -> DBReport : findOrFail(reportId)
activate DBReport
DBReport --> Maker : SavedReport Model
deactivate DBReport

Maker -> Request : fromJson(savedReport->payload)
activate Request
Request -> Serializer : fromJson(json)
activate Serializer
Serializer --> Request : ReportRequest Object (AST)
deactivate Serializer
Request --> Maker : ReportRequest Object
deactivate Request

Maker --> Client : ReportRequest Object
deactivate Maker

note right of Client
  Client uses the structured ReportRequest
  object to seamlessly repopulate the
  frontend Report Builder UI.
end note

@enduml
